  <meta name="assert" content="In this test, the ic unit is the advance height measure of the 水 (CJK water ideograph, U+6C32769) glyph.">

  <style>
  @font-face
    {
      font-family: IcTestFullWidth;
      src: url(resources/IcTestFullWidth.woff2);
    }

  div
    {
      float: left;
      font-family: IcTestFullWidth;
      font-size: 80px; /* arbitrary font size */
      writing-mode: vertical-rl;
    }

  div#test-blue
    {
      background-color: blue;
      height: 5ic;
      width: 1.8em;
    }

  div#reference-orange
    {
      background-color: orange;
      color: orange;
      line-height: 1.8; /* arbitrary line-height */
    }
  </style><p><p>

  <p><p>Test passes if there is a blue rectangle with the <strong>same height</strong> as an orange rectangle.

